dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents parks for the City of Madison, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Madison_City_Parks_2014.gdb. Other feature classes in this geodatabase include: Botanical_Gardens, Cemeteries, Golf_Courses, Land_polygons, Mall_Concourse, Park_Name, and Zoo.
